name: Experiment Or Die #96
description: Project to create a new collage every day for a year using my years of personal assets. Tonights design, the last one of the year, is about peace and love. The crypto space has been incredibly inviting and hopefully with however the space is going to change and evolve in the next 6 months to a year we can nurture and maintain this inclusive and supportive ethos.
